    <div class="w-6/12 mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-5xl">About</h1>
        <img src="/public/images/memoji.png" class="my-2 drop-shadow-[10px_10px_35px_rgba(39,245,131,0.3)]"/>
        <p>
            Hello! My name is John Doe, and I'm a Network Engineer with over 5 years of experience in the industry. I am passionate about creating reliable and efficient network solutions that solve real-world problems and simplify people's lives.
          </p><br />
